---
// Hero section with eyebrow, headline, description and CTAs
---

<div class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow" data-i18n="eyebrow">Senior Backend Engineer · Wrocław, Poland</p>
  <h1 data-i18n="h1">Systems built to <em>last</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-desc" data-i18n="hero-desc">
    I build the backend systems that make products work — reliable, scalable, ready for production. 7 years of experience, from architecture to delivery. Got a project? Let's talk.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-ctas">
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary" data-i18n="cta-contact">Get in touch →</a>
    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/maciek-bartosik" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-ghost">LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: -200px;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(74, 240, 160, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s forwards;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    color: var(--heading);
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s forwards;
  }

  h1 :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--body);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s forwards;
  }
</style>
